title: Nevertrending Story 12/14: Electoral College, Cleveland, Dr. Jill Biden, New Zealand, Charley Pride

description:
On this edition of the Nevertrending Story Jack and Miles discuss the Electoral College confirming Biden's victory for the millionth time, the Cleveland Baseball team has finally decided to rebrand, a dumbass WSJ article asked Dr. Jill Biden to drop the Doctor title because.....????, New Zealand has one (1) new COVID case from an airliner worker traveling in America, and Country Music Legend Charley Pride has passed away due to complications from COVID.
